Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我问得哑口无言就让我堕天？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个神当得心眼也太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不听人劝可是变老的开始啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐了几十亿年的位子 老糊涂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.96,0:00:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那个米迦勒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亏我平时那么照顾她 说翻脸就翻脸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才是万年老二啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人界也好 地狱也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.43,0:00:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去就去 谁怕谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.23,0:01:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.86,0:01:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能看到我？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.53,0:01:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先止血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.99,0:01:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人 普通的人类？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.50,0:01:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.34,0:01:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 血止住了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.84,0:01:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.05,0:01:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.85,0:01:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去也不是办法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去叫人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.35,0:01:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是天使
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.19,0:01:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类是看不见我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.94,0:01:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能看到我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:01:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.32,0:02:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十束真莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真莉亚 你运气不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使的性命托付给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.97,0:02:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.61,0:02:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真莉亚 你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想快点成为大罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾乃七宗罪之一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫉妒的魔王利维坦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说着玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:02:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 贝希摩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帅不帅？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 利维会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.54,0:03:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个十字架
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有天使被堕天了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是天使吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是路西法大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使排名第一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望堕天的天使排名第一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想欺负的天使排名第一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人称天使赞歌之王的路西法大人 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我仰慕死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在天界被人嫌弃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了地狱反倒受人追捧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是任何东西都会冻住的地狱最底层科赛特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么东西都是又冰又硬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有冻不住的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又冰又硬…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来去的地方深得不能再深了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荷埃尤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烫 烫死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使的衣服被荷埃尤喷出的热水溶解了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛苦是家常便饭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大天使路西法大入该不会坚持不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个 丝一般柔滑的肌肤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好羡慕 好嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通红通红的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让利维帮你治好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 变态
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不老实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在利维面前坦诚一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实多了呀 好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利维可喜欢大天使路西法大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 干脆我们一起征服整个地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利维就能当上大罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会上你的当
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且现在天堂地狱和我没任何关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱干嘛干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利维认识的路西法大人温柔帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会答应我做任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有时候睥气差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是消气以后随我怎么撒娇她都不嫌烦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她必须这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,软绵绵的攻击 怎么可能管用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都快上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的能力不过如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本伤不了我分毫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傲慢的大天使路西法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我主伟大 赐命于我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消灭路西法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神要消灭我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要偿还你的罪孽“傲慢”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永世不得解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮得到你嘲笑我？米迦勒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我 米迦勒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帅！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美丽 强大 令人妒忌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是谜得人家都湿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱死姐姐大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫利维啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司掌水元素的魔王利维坦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会永远陪在姐姐大人身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人要君临七宗罪之首
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把利维连同整个地狱都变成你的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要发火了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少得寸进尺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲密接触也很重要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.02,0:08:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲密接触很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要说两遍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正今后要在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在说清楚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
