Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:08:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是万魔殿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,统治地狱的七宗罪集结于此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住 天使
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是愤怒的魔王 撒旦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不是区区天使可以来的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖被我等消灭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是谁在偷偷摸摸地监视天使
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢瞧不起我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到能躲过我的斧头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是个能打的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也挺能打
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过下手还不够狠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在这里
