Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长得挺可爱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道浪起来是什么声音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:33.65,Sin Name,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn@FZYaSong-B-GBK\frz-90\pos(16,555.857)}\N暴食
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:38.61,Sin Name,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn@FZYaSong-B-GBK\frz-90\pos(16,557.856)}\N怠惰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使？无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:43.58,Sin Name,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn@FZYaSong-B-GBK\frz-90\pos(1822,551.856)}\N愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们就是七宗罪？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,统治地狱的七大魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 好像少了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利维坦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我欣赏你给别人带路的一片好心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你是不是忘了 只有大罪可以出入这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利维有姐姐大人在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我剁碎了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好搞清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁才是大罪之首
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你忘了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打听别入身份之前不应该自己先报上家门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在问你话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在区区天使面前介绍自己着实令人不快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.62,0:11:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地狱中无人不知的第一名门
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班德尔家的千金
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:12:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最为华丽 最为美艳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太长了 浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何等傲慢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是虚荣的魔王 贝利尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放肆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是七宗罪的顶点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:19.92,Sin Name,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn@FZYaSong-B-GBK\frz-90\pos(1822,553.857)}\N虚荣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虚荣的魔王 贝利尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自称大人 真不害臊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天上也有一个和她一样臭屁的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,言归正传
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使来这里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是路西法姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路西法？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天界七美德之首吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路西法竟然堕入地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是出了多大的丑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使生性狡诈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计是打着堕天的幌子 攻打地狱来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想骗过我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宗罪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:12:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉她！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我亲自送你上路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路西法这种小角色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人足够
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囗气不小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就如利维坦所愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我路西法要打败你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站在七宗罪之首
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真莉亚你就喜欢和天使有关的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 从小就喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道 耳朵都听出茧了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美菜 你觉得真的有天使存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们学校的确是教会学校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.21,0:13:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我也不敢确定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是真的有天使 我倒想见一面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问一句Hey,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:13:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you 天使?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能信的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过如旲有天使 那也肯定会有恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说过去有个恐怖的大王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:22.91,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,诺查丹玛斯关于1999年世界末日来临的预言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美菜说话就是不着调
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教堂那次事故以后你就有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们都是怪胎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以有什么烦恼尽管来找我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们祈求 就给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:43.30,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,马太福音第七章第七节
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.14,0:14:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 美菜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.73,0:14:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会有天使 一定是我在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美菜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要摸入屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.57,0:14:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.61,0:14:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手不自觉地就往你的安产型屁股伸过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.99,0:15:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真莉亚 为我生猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋美菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就凭你也想坐上七宗罪之首的位子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废话少说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.76,0:15:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班德尔家代代相传的魔剑 达因史雷夫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:22.30,Default - Append,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1296,997.999)}Dáinsleif
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌入彻底断气之前决不会回到剑鞘中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千之默示
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:30.23,Default - Append,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(958.5,997.715)}Thousand of Apocalypse
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我班德尔家代代相传的魔剑达因史雷夫！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么鬼 便宜货吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性格烂的人记性也不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过我已经不是天使
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.61,0:16:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说这战利品 哪来的地摊货
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢藐视我班德尔家 饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个天使好强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实力仅次于撒旦的贝利尔居然毫无还手之力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.21,0:16:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝利尔干什么都是老二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.88,0:16:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学而不精
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是要靠我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才明明被打得落花流水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.18,0:16:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝利尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我 诺斯底
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不忍看到小姐衣着单薄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.90,0:16:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请用我的身体避寒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿全心全意保护您的安危
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.21,0:17:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堕天使 尝尝我的绝招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以首领贝利尔之名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令七宗罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将堕天使路西法拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管把她伤成什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.61,0:17:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我领头功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.66,0:17:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撒旦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许抢我风头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯蒙 不要脸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是色欲的阿斯蒙蒂斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就想尝尝天使是什么滋味了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反应很有趣哦 真让人兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯蒙蒂斯 不要多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有利维才可以和姐姐大人做这种下流的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.59,0:18:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给这个不知天高地厚的混账天使
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来一次全套的地狱之苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:19:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么还留恋着过去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为这对天使的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才会被你们这些贱人欺负
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 那你可得准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也来试试 很好玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提不起劲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.63,0:19:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性格这么扭曲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.89,0:19:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交手就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样蹂躏对手我可不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一只
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.48,0:19:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭出来没事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要以为很好受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在痛苦中挣扎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:19:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后似乎会发生许多有趣的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 七宗罪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你斩断了神给我的重轭 贝利尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾乃路西法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,违抗神明 背负傲慢之罪名的魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.19,0:20:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冥府被打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.32,0:20:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流放吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的地估计是人界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.78,0:20:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区天使 也不掂掂自己的斤两
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她长出了象征魔王的犄角
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的路西法 饶不了你
